{"tid":2338512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"揭公安嚴刑逼供 律師面臨釘牌  周澤：憂寒蟬效應 當局更濫權","createTime":"2020-12-24T05:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T05:28:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc1775b9023152b8e56629733cabcfc59f4323f","tid":2338512,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201224/BQ4IPV2I3VDZLMHSDDE6TZ34VA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201224%2FBQ4IPV2I3VDZLMHSDDE6TZ34VA%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76McFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=dcd209dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201224%2FBQ4IPV2I3VDZLMHSDDE6TZ34VA%2F&h=812b0801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201224/BQ4IPV2I3VDZLMHSDDE6TZ34VA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n揭公安嚴刑逼供 律師面臨釘牌 <br />\n周澤：憂寒蟬效應 當局更濫權<br />\n<br />\n內地著名刑事辯護律師周澤被指早前在安徽律師呂先三詐騙案中，為呂先三擔任辯護律師時，曾對外披露兩段另一被告邵柏春被辦案公安刑訊逼供的片段，當局認為此舉涉及違法，故擬對周作出停止執業一年的行政處罰，事件引起國內律師界關注。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：藝術家聲援佔中判囚1年8個月<br />\n<br />\n北京市朝陽區司法局本周一（21日）發出的《行政處罰聽證告知書》顯示，周澤在今年1月17日曾透過微博「周澤拍案」發表題為〈合肥公安辦呂先三律師的套路〉的文章，文中並附上辦案公安審訊時的截圖片段。當局認為周此舉是「以不正當方式影響依法辦理案件的違法行為」，故擬對他作出停止執業一年的行政處罰，周澤目前已收到聽證告知書。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hDhvXTLfRqxomCzUNvfk14Ag7ro=/1000x677/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AH5AEA23DJB2HFLVRE6ONRHT34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhDhvXTLfRqxomCzUNvfk14Ag7ro%3D%2F1000x677%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAH5AEA23DJB2HFLVRE6ONRHT34.jpg&h=3628546c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周澤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後被告刑期大減<br />\n<br />\n據悉，安徽律師呂先三被指於2014年，受案中另外兩名被告徐維琴、邵柏春兩夫婦所托，代理他們過去牽涉的民間借貸案，其間夫婦兩人再捲入借貸糾紛，並涉暴力催債等指控，呂先三卻因此視為共犯，其後被控參加黑社會性質組織罪及詐騙罪，呂先三去年10月一審被判囚12年。其後，呂先三的代表律師周澤獲取到邵柏春在公安機關接受訊問的片段，發現邵柏春當時曾遭公安多次按壓扣在其手上的手銬23秒，邵柏春當時表現痛苦，大有用刑逼供之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n周澤其後在今年1月在。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據周澤向本報表示，對於當。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，律師的功能本來就。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過他強調包括這宗案件在內，自。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Mc9YgicrHtPbC4CIL0rb95Pkmqs=/1917x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XFDNAFQG65CDXFTORIRWEG7F5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMc9YgicrHtPbC4CIL0rb95Pkmqs%3D%2F1917x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXFDNAFQG65CDXFTORIRWEG7F5I.jpg&h=cb0ab24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■公安按壓被告人的手銬，以嚴刑逼供。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/59IC6nI6P17vJPiWpaikKKKiSNk=/1587x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3MCMEFSF2BC3ZNRCVEMBVDV2GQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F59IC6nI6P17vJPiWpaikKKKiSNk%3D%2F1587x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3MCMEFSF2BC3ZNRCVEMBVDV2GQ.jpg&h=f32a541f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■書法家揮毫，為周澤抱打不平。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾為蒙冤記者學者辯護<br />\n<br />\n周澤恐面臨停業一年的處罰，事件震驚國內法律界。據北京大學法學院教授張千帆接受本報訪問時指，因為周澤所披露的事件是真實發生的，而最終影響到刑期變輕，而周只是維護當事人的權利，這是不公平的處罰。<br />\n<br />\n他又形容事件開了壞先例，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n周澤是內地著名刑事辯護律。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/微博<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tLssmNVRbWJip_vlkfbdIAANcLM=/749x741/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3EIEG5DROFG5DEASNUMFTZWJHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtLssmNVRbWJip_vlkfbdIAANcLM%3D%2F749x741%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3EIEG5DROFG5DEASNUMFTZWJHA.jpg&h=c5295595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QRerV1z3z_GzNNoKgbrrdThbVU8=/542x702/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G2KSZTIIXVBUVGORGNDRQHRDL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQRerV1z3z_GzNNoKgbrrdThbVU8%3D%2F542x702%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG2KSZTIIXVBUVGORGNDRQHRDL4.jpg&h=f037d821&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}